[00:11.39]Before the mountains learned to stand
[00:15.79]Before the oceans kissed the land
[00:20.18]You spoke the dark into the light
[00:24.58]And every star obeyed Your might
[00:28.98]The heavens shake at just Your name
[00:33.37]Angels veil their eyes in flame
[00:37.77]No throne compares, no power stays
[00:42.17]Before the Ancient of all days
[00:46.56]Not love alone, not grace alone
[00:50.96]But fire and light around Your throne
[00:55.36]You are not common, You are not near
[00:59.75]Unless You draw us through holy fear
[01:04.15]Holy, Holy, Holy is the Lord
[01:08.55]Set apart, eternal, unmatched, adored
[01:12.94]Glory like thunder, mercy like rain
[01:17.34]All of creation cries out Your name
[01:21.74]Holy, Holy, none beside You stands
[01:26.13]The Alpha, Omega, the Great I Am
[01:30.53]We fall undone, yet You invite
[01:34.92]The Holy God, wrapped in light
[01:39.32]The ground is sacred where You are
[01:43.72]Burning bush, consuming fire
[01:48.11]You are not shaped by mortal thought
[01:52.51]You cannot be tamed, controlled, or bought
[01:56.91]Justice rolls from righteous hands
[02:01.30]Truth unbending, perfect plans
[02:05.70]Yet still You call the dust to live
[02:10.10]Still You choose to love, forgive
[02:14.49]The weight of glory bows our knees
[02:18.89]We breathe in awe, we tremble, please
[02:23.29]You are not safe, yet You are good
[02:27.68]The Holy God, misunderstood
[02:32.08]Holy, Holy, Holy is the Lord
[02:36.48]Set apart, eternal, unmatched, adored
[02:40.87]Glory like thunder, mercy like rain
[02:45.27]All of creation cries out Your name
[02:49.66]Holy, Holy, none beside You stands
[02:54.06]The Alpha, Omega, the Great I Am
[02:58.46]We fall undone, yet You invite
[03:02.85]The Holy God, wrapped in light
[03:07.25]Who can stand before Your throne?
[03:11.65]Who can claim You as their own?
[03:16.04]Only by the blood You gave
[03:20.44]Only by the grace that saves
[03:24.84]Fire and mercy intertwine
[03:29.23]Justice kissed by love divine
[03:33.63]Heaven roars, the veil is torn
[03:38.03]The Holy One, yet not withdrawn
[03:42.42]Holy, Holy, Holy is the Lord
[03:46.82]Earth and heaven now respond
[03:51.22]King of glory, fear and flame
[03:55.61]Every knee bows to Your name
[04:00.01]Holy, Holy, forever You reign
[04:04.41]Time itself speaks You remain
[04:08.80]We fall undone, yet You invite
[04:13.20]The Holy God, wrapped in light
[04:17.59]Holy beyond measure
[04:21.99]Holy beyond words
[04:26.39]Holy forever
[04:30.78]You are the Lord
